The RUDSET Institute will be organising a 45-day free residential training for unemployed youth in computer DTP on its premises at Brahmavar in Udupi district from January 25 to March 9.A press release issued by the institute here said that the training had been approved by the Union Ministry of Rural Development. Unemployed youth from Udupi, Shivamogga and Uttara Kannada districts in the age group of 18 to 45 and aspiring to become self-employed, can apply.Interested candidates can send their applications to the Director, RUDSET Institute, 52nd Heroor, Brahmavar, Udupi â€“ 576 213. For details, call 0820-2563455 or log on to: www.